<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>,</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. If this was you, you can proceed with the password change by clicking the link below:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>If you did not initiate this request, please disregard this email.</p>
<p>Your password will remain unchanged unless you access the provided link and create a new one.</p>

<p>Thank you.</p>

<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>The Mogul Team</p>





